<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٦٣٠٩ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/598">إِسْحَاقُ: </a>أَخْبَرَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1270">حَبَّانُ: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6739">هَمَّامٌ: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5183">قَتَادَةُ: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/822">أَنَسُ بْنُ مَالِكٍ، </a>عَنِ النَّبِيِّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> وَحَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6669">هُدْبَةُ: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6739">هَمَّامٌ: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5183">قَتَادَةُ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/822">أَنَسٍ </a><span class="special">﵁</span> قَالَ: قَالَ رَسُولُ اللهِ <span class="special">ﷺ</span>: <span class="c2">«اللهُ أَفْرَحُ بِتَوْبَةِ عَبْدِهِ مِنْ أَحَدِكُمْ سَقَطَ عَلَى بَعِيرِهِ وَقَدْ أَضَلَّهُ فِي أَرْضِ فَلَاةٍ.»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>